─── Activation Steps (ADT / SAP BTP ABAP Environment) ───────────────────────

1. Open ADT → your BTP ABAP project.
2. File → New → Other → ABAP → Business Services → Service Binding
     Name        : ZUIS_TESTFORCLASS_O4
     Description : ZTEST FOR CLASS OData V4 UI binding
     Binding Type: OData V4 - UI
     Service Def : ZUIS_TESTFORCLASS
3. Click "Publish" to activate the binding.
4. Under "Service Version 0001" expand entity set "TESTFORCLASS".
5. Click "Preview" → Fiori Elements List Report launches.

